summary: This is the Poem that chooses You
title: This is the Poem that chooses You
body: The Palace of wants took them…  fruits and sweets and hatred within filled then overflowed..chaos swept smooth a new world. YOU with ME in an ancient afternoon..swimming in a fever of each other.  the WORD in our Hearts traveled everywhere alone.
